por gentileza, jogue de volta.

244
00:16:13,707 --> 00:16:15,000
Bom sujeito.

245
00:16:18,211 --> 00:16:19,421
Tchau.

246
00:16:27,053 --> 00:16:28,054
Tem certeza?

247
00:16:29,556 --> 00:16:30,557
Tenho.

248
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:38,148
Primeiro os mais velhos.

249
00:18:25,964 --> 00:18:27,132
